abstract: >
  AI Business Skills is a modular Markdown-based toolkit of AI Skills that transforms
  general-purpose Large Language Models (Claude, ChatGPT, Gemini, Copilot) into
  specialized business assistants for online entrepreneurs. Includes 16 production-ready
  marketing skills calibrated for Vietnamese market (2025–2026 benchmarks) with a
  Global Edition rolling out Q2–Q4 2026. Three modules: Marketing (live), Dropshipping
  (Q2 2026), Personal Branding (Q3 2026). MIT licensed.
